This repository vendors copies of the official Loops agent skills for
zero-step install (so `/plugin install promptmetrics-newsletter@promptmetrics`
brings them along without a separate curl/npx step). The vendored skills are
distributed upstream under the MIT License and are reproduced here under that
license's permission, with attribution:

  Source repository : https://github.com/Loops-so/skills
  Pinned ref        : v0.2.0
  Upstream license  : MIT (Copyright (c) 2026 Loops)
  Vendored skills   : skills/loops-api/
                      skills/loops-cli/
                      skills/loops-lmx/
                      skills/loops-email-sending-best-practices/

Each vendored SKILL.md carries a header comment pointing back to its upstream
file for drift-tracing. Do not edit the vendored skills in place; update
upstream and re-run the maintainer sync:

    ./skills/newsletter/scripts/sync-loops-skills.sh [ref]   # default: v0.2.0

Each vendored skill directory contains a copy of the upstream MIT LICENSE
(skills/loops-{api,cli,lmx,email-sending-best-practices}/LICENSE), retaining
the upstream "Copyright (c) 2026 Loops" notice as required by the MIT License.